originalText.text: In addition to double charging me in the past, after performing a cosmetic laser procedure, Ellen Marmur charged me for both the laser procedure AND a full medical visit because she spent about 1 minute at the end asking her assistant to write a Rx for a medication I’d previously told her I had a bad reaction to. If that weren’t enough, she aggressively pushes the products she sells in her office on me. She is completely two-faced.
